name: Clear Minded Hockey Jersey - Preorder ONLY
description:
Burgundy and white NHL Jerseys from Reebok with a sewn patch front logo, and heat pressed custom numbers and names. THESE ARE LIMITED TO PREORDER ONLY.

Professionally manufactured with the highest quality specifically for us. 

Team Clear Minded!

These jerseys are the second in our hockey jersey series that started around this time in 2012. 

These jerseys will have custom names and numbers on the back (#00-99). At checkout, in the "Notes to Seller" box enter the name on the back exactly how you'd like it to appear, and the number you'd like. If you have difficulty finding this box, just send your name and size via email to info@clearmindedclothing.com. Be sure to double check, because these are custom and you will not be refunded for errors on your part.

Sizing is about the same as ordering a hoodie.

**THIS ITEM IS CUSTOM AND PREORDER ONLY. ORDERS ARE EXPECTED TO BE DELIVERED AROUND CHRISTMAS BUT HOLIDAY DELIVERY IS NOT GUARANTEED. DO NOT DELAY ORDERING, IT ONLY DELAYS PRODUCTION. IF YOU'D LIKE TO ORDER ANOTHER PRODUCT WITH THIS JERSEY PLEASE ORDER SEPARATELY FROM THE JERSEY!**

name: Orthodox - End of My Wit CD (Hardcore)
description:

Stream it before you buy it, here: http://clearmindedrecords.bandcamp.com/album/orthodox-end-of-my-wit

"End Of My Wit is written about my personal experiences with suicide, depression, addiction, anger and anxiety. That being said:
This album is for anyone who has ever fallen victim to actions stricken from the hands of an addict.

You Do Not Deserve It. You Are Not To Blame."

-Orthodox
